data.description: Beautiful property featuring 4.47 acres. This remarkable piece of land offers a perfect setting for a mobile home, making it an ideal opportunity for those seeking a tranquil and spacious living environment. The presence of mature trees adds to the charm and natural beauty of the surroundings, creating a peaceful and serene atmosphere.  On the property is a 20 x 40 shop with roll-up doors and commercial grade electrical, further enhancing its versatility and potential. An insulated office/room with a half bath is attached to the shop. The spacious shop is perfect for a multitude of uses and provides endless possibilities.  The shop also has a large covered area with 30 & 50 amp hookups. Ideal for storing your campers, boats, trailers, or RVs, ensuring that your recreational vehicles are always protected and ready for your next adventure.  With no restrictions, you have the freedom to transform this land into your dream oasis, create a thriving business, or simply enjoy the space for your personal pursuits.
